PRINCE OF PERSIA 2: The Shadow and The Flame
by Sierra On-Line.  Interactive Demo.
Preview the eagerly awaited sequel to the
award winning Price of Persia.  View or Play
the first level of this awesome cinematic
action game. VGA. Hard Disk required. 640K
RAM minimum.  2MB of RAM for digital sounds.
Sound Blaster, Sound Blaster Pro, Pro Audio
Spectrum, and 100% compatibles.
